snippet.title: Johnny Depp Loses Libel Case
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp loses case today! GEEK WHAT?!'s reaction & breakdown of the verdict. Judge sides with Amber Heard. Depp gets fired from Fantastic Beasts 3! Heard is still in Aquaman 2 as of now?
Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/c/GEEKWHATInc

Johnny Depp Verdict BREAKDOWN today! GEEK WHAT?!  host MatKat83’s reaction & breakdown!  Johnny Depp loses cases against Amber Heard and The Sun in the UK.  Depp is then fired from Fantastic Beasts 3! What does this mean for Aquaman 2? Share your own reaction to Johnny Depp verdict! And be sure to make GEEK WHAT?! your number 1 stop for movie and entertainment news here on YouTube today!
